title: Al-Qaida, Al-Qaeda recruitment handbook
description:
A video clip from the U.S. corporate media about an "Al-Qaida" recruitment manual.

A PDF of a web document describing this subject.

The video is 640x480 and in Ogg/Vorbis format.

The video looks just like the picture you see on this page. It was recorded with a video camera aimed at a TV screen. It's not pretty, but it is enough to let you hear and see this story.

Read the text file for more information.
